GBFeature_quals.GBQualifier_value: SAMN04457443 Colubrid snake Xenodon merremi cDNA library

Organ: venom glands; Vector: pSPORT-1; Site_1: SalI; Site_2: NotI; 5ug of mRNA from X. merremi venom glands were primed with oligo-(dT) Not-I and reverse transcribed to cDNA using Superscript Plasmid System for cDNA Synthesis and Cloning (Invitrogen). The cDNAs were selected by size (350-600 pb and up 600 pb) in agarose gel electrophoresis, linked to Sal I adapters and directionally cloned in pSPORT-1 vector.
